Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好的朋友Tommy\N{\fs38}Your best friend -- Tommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们知道了 别显摆发生在你身边的谋杀案了\N{\fs38}We know. STop true-crime bragging.
