Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟自己说Tommy只是在\N{\fs38}I just told myself that Tommy had gotten lost
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙果乐园的魔法世界里迷路了\N{\fs38}in the magical realm of Froopyland.
