Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 - 仙果乐园\N{\fs38}What? -Froopyland.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我最得意的作品吗 不敢说\N{\fs38}Was it my best work? I don’t know.
