Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你决定你要回来的时候\N{\fs38}The moment you decide to come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我按下开关 克隆体就完成了它的任务\N{\fs38}I flip a switch, and the clone’s job is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不会感受到痛苦 也不会后悔\N{\fs38}It feels no pain, it regrets nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.93,0:18:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会发生"银翼杀手"里的事情\N{\fs38}and has zero chance of going “Blade Runner.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一切都不重要 为什么你要为我做这些\N{\fs38}If nothing matters, why would you do that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 也许你太不重要了 以至于我喜欢你\N{\fs38}I don’t know, maybe you matter so little that I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者这让你变得重要\N{\fs38}Or maybe it makes you matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我爱你\N{\fs38}Maybe I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许因为你的妈妈\N{\fs38}Maybe something about your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要得寸进尺\N{\fs38}Don’t jump a gift shark in the mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道我能不能做到\N{\fs38}I don’t know if I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么留下来 好好享受生活\N{\fs38}Then stay and luxuriate in a life
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最终会明白你选择了什么\N{\fs38}you can finally know you’ve chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小经验是不管你选择了什么\N{\fs38}My secret bonus is that no matter what you choose,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最终都会适应\N{\fs38}you’re finally gonna chill the fuck out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs38}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我要做什么了\N{\fs38}I know what I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊\N{\fs38}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs38}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃不了的\N{\fs38}You can’t run forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是真的被惹毛了\N{\fs38}She’s really pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:18:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 还有点撩人呢\N{\fs38}I know. It's kinda hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fs38}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是狩猎者们 他们回来了 快跑\N{\fs38}The hunters! They’re back! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.48,0:19:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是狩猎者 - 我们想和你们躲在一起\N{\fs38}We’re not hunters. -We want to hide with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是在躲藏 我们在筑巢\N{\fs38}We’re not hiding. We’re nesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了吧你\N{\fs38}Ooh Ia Ia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个孩子必须被消灭\N{\fs38}The children must be destroyed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们才能在一起\N{\fs38}so that we can be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该用正确的方式跟她分手 爸爸\N{\fs38}You need to break up with her, Dad -- properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的 爸\N{\fs38}God damn it, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甩了她\N{\fs38}Dump her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行 行\N{\fs38}Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kiara 我们直接远走高飞吧\N{\fs38}Kiara, let’s just run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸 - 说什么呢\N{\fs38}Dad! -Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就有话直说吧\N{\fs38}Just rip the Band-Aid off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行行行\N{\fs38}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kiara 我跟你说我的孩子们是狭隘的种族主义者\N{\fs38}Kiara, when I told you my kids were bigoted racists
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚决要我跟你分手的时候\N{\fs38}who were demanding I break up with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我撒谎了\N{\fs38}I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有人该被用念力掐死\N{\fs38}If anybody deserves to be telekinetically strangled,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该是我\N{\fs38}it’s me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是那个想分手的人\N{\fs38}I’m the one who wants to break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我不是个邪恶的人\N{\fs38}I’m not an evil person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又懒 又懦弱\N{\fs38}I’m lazy, I’m cowardly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 而且我也不知道我在干嘛\N{\fs38}and -- and I do not know what I’m doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 我让某个人在17岁的时候就怀孕了\N{\fs38}Look, I got someone pregnant at 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在办理离婚手续 这些都不是我故意造成的\N{\fs38}We’re getting a divorce. None of this is on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对能和酷的人约会很兴奋\N{\fs38}I was excited to date someone cool
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这能让我的前妻注意到我\N{\fs38}because it would make my ex notice me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对人类是彻底失望了\N{\fs38}I would expect nothing less from humanity --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:20:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类就是自私的 爱操纵别人的 不诚实的物种\N{\fs38}a selfish, manipulative, dishonest species that --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kiara吗 - Trandor\N{\fs38}Kiara? -Trandor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这儿干什么\N{\fs38}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就 狩猎啊\N{\fs38}Just...hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的指望我相信\N{\fs38}Do you really expect me to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和我们之间的事情无关吗\N{\fs38}it has nothing to do with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明知道地球是我的地盘\N{\fs38}You knew Earth was my domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜欢你的弦外之音\N{\fs38}I don’t like what you’re insinuating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸 我们能走了吗 - 等一下\N{\fs38}Dad, can we go now? -Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在觉得我才是备胎\N{\fs38}I’m starting to get the feeling that I was the rebound.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸 刚有人从天而降为你解围\N{\fs38}Dad, you just got handed an ex machina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就接受吧\N{\fs38}You’re taking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Varrix的巢穴遍布300个星系\N{\fs38}Varrix nests spread across 300 galaxies,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就恰好选了这个行星来捕猎吗\N{\fs38}and you just happened to pick this planet to hunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扯得跟蛇怪似的 完全是蛇怪扯\N{\fs38}That’s Gorgon shit -- total Gorgon shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到家啦\N{\fs38}We’re home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 回来啦 - 晚饭吃什么啊\N{\fs38}Hey, guys! -What’s for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry家怎么样 - 老样子\N{\fs38}How was Jerry’s? -The usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能吃披萨吗 - 听起来棒极了\N{\fs38}Can we have pizza? -Pizza sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 Rick 你知道我爸正在和一个外星人约会吗\N{\fs38}Hey, Rick, did you know my dad was dating an alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 真恶心 替那个外星人恶心\N{\fs38}No. Gross. For the alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真扫兴 我觉得阿纳尔多披萨店关门了\N{\fs38}Aw, crap, I think Arnaldo’s is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们确定想吃披萨吗\N{\fs38}Are you guys sure you want pizza?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿纳尔多披萨店在那个\N{\fs38}Arnaldo’s isn’t closed in the dimension
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没发明夏令时的次元没关门哦\N{\fs38}where they didn’t invent Daylight Savings!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有你可怎么办啊 我爱你 爸爸\N{\fs38}What would we do without you? I love you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你 宝贝\N{\fs38}Love you, too, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 这不是时间旅行\N{\fs38}By the way, that wasn’t time travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.35,0:21:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在柜台上有些披萨\N{\fs38}There were just a couple pizzas on the counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就拿过来了\N{\fs38}I grabbed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 Jerry 我是Kiara\N{\fs38}Hey, Jerry, it’s Kiara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 我男朋友看见了那些你给我发的短信\N{\fs38}Listen, my boyfriend saw those texts you’ve been sending me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.14,0:21:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他特别生气\N{\fs38}and he got pretty pissed off
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他打给你 忽略他就好了\N{\fs38}If he calls you, just ignore him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是Carmox\N{\fs38}This is Carmox.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我截获了你和我的新女友Kiara\N{\fs38}I have intercepted sexual communications
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之间的挑逗短信\N{\fs38}between you and my new girlfriend, Kiara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在要去杀了你\N{\fs38}I am coming to kill you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呦 Jerry 我是老R\N{\fs38}RICK: Yo, Jerry, it’s the Big R.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀了那个要来追杀你的外星人\N{\fs38}Uh, I killed that alien that was coming after ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.65,0:21:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为你保驾护航哦 兄弟\N{\fs38}Looking out for ya, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.03,0:21:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 Jerry 我是Rick\N{\fs38}Hey, Jerry, it’s Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别生气我上了你的前女友Kiara\N{\fs38}Don’t be mad. I fucked your ex-girifriend Kiara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.78,0:22:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在跟谁说话 Rick\N{\fs38}KIARA: Who are you talking to, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不重要\N{\fs38}Doesn’t matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.91,0:22:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 Jerry 我是Michael\N{\fs38}Hey, Jerry, this is Michael
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古董电话租赁的员工\N{\fs38}down at The Antique Phone rentals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,额 我不打算再追究了 也不打算要回\N{\fs38}Urn, I’m gonna go ahead and let you off the hook
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.37,0:22:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你七十美元的滞纳金了\N{\fs38}for the $70 late fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以继续留着那个答录机\N{\fs38}You can go ahead and keep that answering machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.46,0:22:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正现在基本也没人用这个了\N{\fs38}Nobody really uses those anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非是电视节目上的展示环节\N{\fs38}except for exposition on TV shows, anyways.
